  "detailed_description": "<h1>Picture books on sale now!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337290/extras/f977afa784f9c8d7ee63d89e1b4bdabb.avif?t=1763361561\" width=512 height=128 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>A story about the adventures of Ruku and Lish With a heart balloon made from a flower puzzle How far can they go?<br>A cute adventure story about a rabbit, Ruku, and a cat, Lish, just like in a picture book.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make a \"heart balloon\" with the flower puzzle.<br>How far can you fly in the sky?</h2><br><br>Easy puzzle game to collect flowers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337290/extras/f13a1df5bbe66fd762e2dbde20735189.avif?t=1763361561\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find two or more flowers of the same color next to each other.<br></li><li>Press \"A button / Enter key\" or \"touch\" when you find it.</li></ul>Now you can collect flowers and make heart balloons.<br>Let's make as many heart balloons as our target number!<br><br><br>And much more.<br><strong>Free Mode\" to continue to create heart balloons</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337290/extras/9734a0ebcd81e984a2ee481692654a04.avif?t=1763361561\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br><br><strong>Turn all the flowers that appear into heart balloons! Puzzle Mode</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337290/extras/eec6e85c3740c287f3e0386991fdc44c.avif?t=1763361561\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br><br><strong>Gallery\" where you can see extra illustrations and sheet music</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337290/extras/0d6e021530d3017db81dd292b12876fa.avif?t=1763361561\" width=512 height=288 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>A story about the adventures of Ruku and Lish With a heart balloon made from a flower puzzle How far can they go?<br>A cute adventure story about a rabbit, Ruku, and a cat, Lish, just like in a picture book.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make a \"heart balloon\" with the flower puzzle.<br>How far can you fly in the sky?</h2><br><br>Easy puzzle game to collect flowers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337290/extras/f13a1df5bbe66fd762e2dbde20735189.avif?t=1763361561\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find two or more flowers of the same color next to each other.<br></li><li>Press \"A button / Enter key\" or \"touch\" when you find it.</li></ul>Now you can collect flowers and make heart balloons.<br>Let's make as many heart balloons as our target number!<br><br><br>And much more.<br><strong>Free Mode\" to continue to create heart balloons</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337290/extras/9734a0ebcd81e984a2ee481692654a04.avif?t=1763361561\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br><br><strong>Turn all the flowers that appear into heart balloons! Puzzle Mode</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337290/extras/eec6e85c3740c287f3e0386991fdc44c.avif?t=1763361561\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br><br><strong>Gallery\" where you can see extra illustrations and sheet music</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337290/extras/0d6e021530d3017db81dd292b12876fa.avif?t=1763361561\" width=512 height=288 /></span>",
